race.comment: CAVALLO RED (4) ran on strongly over the mile here two back before stretching in trip last start and being just fair. Back to 1500m today looks ideal and Chris Parnham replaces the apprentice hoop. Maps well back in grade and he looks the one to beat. EXTREME LOVE (7) finished off strongly from midfield when 1.5L off the winner. The form out of the race has worked out well and she drops in weight today. Can lob midfield and storm home once again. COLD SHIZZLE (1) finished 1.5L behind last start in much stronger company over the mile here. Hasn't won for a while but is drops right back in grade today and he can return to form. MASTER ALEX (5) missed in a photo finish last start and while this is tougher, his figures stack up off that performance. Can feature in the finish again. LOVA SESSION (2) should get his chance under Pike.
